      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "[SCROLL-DOWN-MAX]"
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "Remarks"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "In the editor and in filelists, scrolls the screen to the"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "extreme in the direction specified.  By default, Ctrl-PgUp"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "and Ctrl-PgDn are assigned with [SCROLL-UP-MAX] and"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "[SCROLL-DOWN-MAX]."
